<text><body>
<lb n="1118c05" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="1118c06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118c07" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 396</head>
<lb n="1118c08" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>佛說法滅盡經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="1118c09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118c10" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="1118060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（僧祐…錄））十三字＝（（僧祐錄失譯））五字【宋】【宮】，（（僧祐錄失譯人今附劉宋錄））十一字【元】【明】</note><app word-count="13" n="1118060"><lem wit="【大】">僧祐錄中失譯經人名今附宋錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">僧祐錄失譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">僧祐錄失譯人今附劉宋錄</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="1118c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118c1101">聞如是。一時佛在拘夷那竭國。如來三月當
<lb n="1118c12" ed="T"/>般涅槃。與諸比丘及諸菩薩。無央數眾來詣
<lb n="1118c13" ed="T"/><note n="1118061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛所＝如來【宮】</note><app n="1118061"><lem wit="【大】">佛所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">如來</rdg></app>稽首于<note n="1118062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">地＋（眷屬圍遶渴仰聞法）【元】【明】</note><app n="1118062"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">地眷屬圍遶渴仰聞法</rdg></app>。世尊寂靜默無所說光明
<lb n="1118c14" ed="T"/>不現。賢者阿難作禮白佛言。<note n="1118063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔世尊〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118063"><lem wit="【大】">世尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>前後說
<lb n="1118c15" ed="T"/>法威光獨顯。今大眾會光更不現。何故如此。
<lb n="1118c16" ed="T"/><note n="1118064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其必有＝必有緣【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其必有＝必有緣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118064"><lem wit="【大】">其必有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">必有緣</rdg></app>故。願聞其意。佛默不應。如是至三
<lb n="1118c17" ed="T"/>佛告阿難。吾涅槃後法欲滅時。五逆濁世魔
<lb n="1118c18" ed="T"/>道興盛。魔作沙門壞亂吾道。著俗衣裳樂好
<lb n="1118c19" ed="T"/>袈裟五色之服。飲酒噉肉殺生貪味。無有
<lb n="1118c20" ed="T"/>慈心更相憎嫉。時有菩薩辟支羅漢。精進修
<pb n="1119a" ed="T" id="T12.0396.1119a"/>
<lb n="1119a01" ed="T"/>德一切敬待。人所宗向教化平等。憐貧念老
<lb n="1119a02" ed="T"/><note n="1119001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鞠＝救【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鞠＝救【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119001"><lem wit="【大】">鞠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">救</rdg></app>育窮厄。琤H經像令人奉事。作諸功德志
<lb n="1119a03" ed="T"/>性<note n="1119002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">恩＝思【元】【明】</note><app n="1119002"><lem wit="【大】">恩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">思</rdg></app>善。不侵害人<note n="1119003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捐＝損【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119003"><lem wit="【大】">捐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">損</rdg></app>身濟物。不自惜己忍
<lb n="1119a04" ed="T"/>辱仁和。設有是人。眾魔比丘咸共<note n="1119004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嫉＝疾【宮】</note><app n="1119004"><lem wit="【大】">嫉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">疾</rdg></app>之誹謗
<lb n="1119a05" ed="T"/>揚惡。擯黜驅遣不令得住。自共於後不修道
<lb n="1119a06" ed="T"/>德。寺廟空荒無復修理轉就毀壞。但貪財物
<lb n="1119a07" ed="T"/>積聚不散不作福德。販賣奴婢耕田種植。焚
<lb n="1119a08" ed="T"/>燒山林傷害眾生無有慈心。奴為比丘。婢為
<lb n="1119a09" ed="T"/>比丘尼。無有道德<note n="1119005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婬&CB00105;＝淫泆【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="1119005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬&CB00105;＝淫泆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1119005"><lem wit="【大】">婬&CB00105;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">淫泆</rdg></app>濁亂男女不別。令道
<lb n="1119a10" ed="T"/>薄淡皆由斯輩。或避縣官依倚吾道。求作沙
<lb n="1119a11" ed="T"/>門不修戒律。月半月盡<note n="1119006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">雖＝假【宮】</note><app n="1119006"><lem wit="【大】">雖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">假</rdg></app>名<note n="1119007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦＝講【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119007"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">講</rdg></app>戒。厭倦懈
<lb n="1119a12" ed="T"/>怠不欲聽聞。<note n="1119008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔抄略前後不肯盡說〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119008"><lem wit="【大】">抄略前後不肯盡說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。經不誦習。
<lb n="1119a13" ed="T"/>設有讀者不識字句。為強言是。不諮明者貢
<lb n="1119a14" ed="T"/>高求名。虛顯雅步以為榮冀望人供養。眾魔
<lb n="1119a15" ed="T"/>比丘命終之後。精神當墮無<note n="1119009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">擇＝澤【宋】</note><app n="1119009"><lem wit="【大】">擇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">澤</rdg></app>地獄。五逆
<lb n="1119a16" ed="T"/>罪中。餓鬼畜生靡不經歷琲e沙劫。罪竟<note n="1119010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乃＝能【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119010"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">能</rdg></app>
<lb n="1119a17" ed="T"/>出生在邊國無三寶處。法欲滅時女人精進
<lb n="1119a18" ed="T"/>琝@<note n="1119011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">功＝福【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">功＝福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119011"><lem wit="【大】">功</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">福</rdg></app>德。男子懈慢不用法語。眼見沙門如
<lb n="1119a19" ed="T"/>視糞土無有信心。法將殄沒。登爾之時諸天
<lb n="1119a20" ed="T"/>泣淚。水旱不調五穀不熟。<note n="1119012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔疫氣流行死亡者眾〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119012"><lem wit="【大】">疫氣流行死亡者
<lb n="1119a21" ed="T"/>眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。人民勤苦縣官<note n="1119013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">計剋＝剋罰【元】【明】</note><app n="1119013"><lem wit="【大】">計剋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">剋罰</rdg></app>。不順道理皆思樂
<lb n="1119a22" ed="T"/>亂。惡人轉多如海中沙。善者甚少若一若二。
<lb n="1119a23" ed="T"/>劫欲盡<note n="1119014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">故＝處【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故＝處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119014"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">處</rdg></app>日月轉<note n="1119015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">短＝促【元】【明】</note><app n="1119015"><lem wit="【大】">短</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">促</rdg></app>人命轉<note n="1119016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">促＝短【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">促＝短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119016"><lem wit="【大】">促</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">短</rdg></app>。四十頭白。
<lb n="1119a24" ed="T"/>男子<app source="1119005" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">婬&CB00105;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">淫泆</rdg></app>精盡夭命。或壽六十。男子壽短女
<lb n="1119a25" ed="T"/>人壽長。七<note n="1119017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">八＝十【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八＝十【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119017"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">十</rdg></app>九十或至百歲。大水忽起卒至
<lb n="1119a26" ed="T"/>無期。世人不信故為有常。眾生雜類<note n="1119018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不問＝無有【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不問＝無有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119018"><lem wit="【大】">不問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">無有</rdg></app>
<lb n="1119a27" ed="T"/><note n="1119019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">豪＝高【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119019"><lem wit="【大】">豪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">高</rdg></app>賤。沒溺<note n="1119020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">浮漂＝流飄【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浮漂＝流飄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119020"><lem wit="【大】">浮漂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">流飄</rdg></app>魚鱉食噉。<note n="1119021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔時有〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119021"><lem wit="【大】">時有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>菩薩辟支
<lb n="1119a28" ed="T"/>羅漢。眾魔驅逐不<note n="1119022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">預＝與【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">預＝與【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119022"><lem wit="【大】">預</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">與</rdg></app>眾會。三乘入山福德之
<lb n="1119a29" ed="T"/>地。恬<note n="1119023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怕＝泊【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1119023"><lem wit="【大】">怕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">泊</rdg></app>自守以為欣快<note n="1119024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔壽命延長〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119024"><lem wit="【大】">壽命延長</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。諸<note n="1119025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＝王【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天＝王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119025"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">王</rdg></app>衛
<pb n="1119b" ed="T" id="T12.0396.1119b"/>
<lb n="1119b01" ed="T"/>護月光出世。得相遭值共興<note n="1119026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吾＝五【宮】</note><app n="1119026"><lem wit="【大】">吾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">五</rdg></app>道。五十二
<lb n="1119b02" ed="T"/>歲。首楞嚴經。般舟三昧。先化滅去。十二部經
<lb n="1119b03" ed="T"/><note n="1119027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尋＝尊【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119027"><lem wit="【大】">尋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">尊</rdg></app>後
<note n="1119028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（復滅…文字））十字＝（（化滅聖王去後））六字【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（復滅…文字））十字＝（（化滅聖王去後））六字【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app word-count="10" n="1119028"><lem wit="【大】">復滅。盡不復現。不見文字</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">化滅聖王去後</rdg></app>。沙門袈裟
<lb n="1119b04" ed="T"/>自然變白。吾法滅時譬如油燈。臨欲滅時光
<lb n="1119b05" ed="T"/><note n="1119029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">明更盛於是便滅＝更明盛【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明更盛於是便滅＝更明盛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119029"><lem wit="【大】">明更盛。於是便滅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">更明盛</rdg></app>。吾法滅時亦如燈滅。自
<lb n="1119b06" ed="T"/>此之後難可數說。如是<note n="1119030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＝又【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119030"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">又</rdg></app>後數千萬歲。彌勒
<lb n="1119b07" ed="T"/>當下世間作佛。天下泰平毒氣消除。雨潤和
<lb n="1119b08" ed="T"/>適五穀滋茂。樹木長大人長八丈。皆壽八萬
<lb n="1119b09" ed="T"/>四千歲。眾生得度不可稱計。賢者阿難作禮
<lb n="1119b10" ed="T"/>白佛。當何名斯經。<note n="1119031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔云何奉持〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔云何奉持〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119031"><lem wit="【大】">云何奉持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。佛言。阿難。
<lb n="1119b11" ed="T"/>此經名為法滅盡。宣告一切宜令分別。功德
<lb n="1119b12" ed="T"/>無量不可稱計。四部弟子聞經悲慘惆悵。皆
<lb n="1119b13" ed="T"/>發無上聖真道意。悉為佛作禮而去。</p>
